OL,3,CD-Day veteran calls for sacrifice of
OL,4,Clife to be recognised by future
OL,5,Cgenerations
OL,7,FHe said: "As one of the last few
OL,8,Fliving witnesses of D-Day, I often
OL,9,Ffind myself wondering about those I
OL,10,Fserved alongside.
OL,12,F"I once had the chance to visit the
OL,13,FNormandy beaches where so many brave
OL,14,Fsouls fought ` that experience will
OL,15,Flive with me forever.
OL,17,F"It's vital we teach future
OL,18,Fgenerations the true cost of freedom
OL,19,Fand ensure they never forget the
OL,20,Fhorrors we faced.
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
