OL,7,FMr Lamond was a signalman on HMS
OL,8,FRowley, part of the 3rd Escort Group,
OL,9,Fwhen it was deployed to rendezvous
OL,10,Fwith battleship HMS Warspite as it
OL,11,Ftravelled to Normandy to shell German
OL,12,Ftroops.
OL,14,FHMS Rowley's role was to act as a
OL,15,Ffirst line of defence by circling HMS
OL,16,FWarspite.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/10
