OL,3,CD-Day veteran calls for sacrifice of
OL,4,Clife to be recognised by future
OL,5,Cgenerations
OL,7,FHe said: "We went up the Normandy
OL,8,Fcoast when I was on the frigate, the
OL,9,FHMS Rowley. The battleship Warspite's
OL,10,Fmission was to soften up all the
OL,11,FNormandy coast by shelling the Nazis
OL,12,Fbut it was our duty to protect it.
OL,14,F"We were constantly getting fired at,
OL,15,Fthe noise was like an express train
OL,16,Fflying right over your head. It was
OL,17,Fterrifying, we were expected to put
OL,18,Four lives on the line.
OL,26,@oD@JOUvD@AOU
