OL,3,CD-Day veteran calls for sacrifice of
OL,4,Clife to be recognised by future
OL,5,Cgenerations
OL,7,F"They went from the sea on to the
OL,8,Fbeach and I saw them disembarking.
OL,9,FThey were being shelled at from all
OL,10,Fangles. Some of them never made it."
OL,12,FHe now lives in McKellar House at
OL,13,FErskine Veterans Village, and had a
OL,14,Fcareer on the railways after leaving
OL,15,Fthe Navy.
OL,17,FWing Commander Ian Cumming said: "It
OL,18,Fis truly an honour to have Albert at
OL,19,FErskine. He is a hero, who risked his
OL,20,Flife for our freedom, and should be
OL,21,Fseen as an inspiration by everyone.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@dO]yD@bOU
