OL,3,CD-Day veteran calls for sacrifice of
OL,4,Clife to be recognised by future
OL,5,Cgenerations
OL,7,F"As we mark this significant
OL,8,Fanniversary, it's crucial that we
OL,9,Fremember not just the sheer scale of
OL,10,Fwhat was achieved during the D-Day
OL,11,Flandings but also the personal
OL,12,Fsacrifices made by each individual
OL,13,Finvolved."
